name: Fire
description: I have no limit to one earthly Soul - from an empty ghost, There is a feeling more holy In it Than insignificant and dumb dust. Who will tell me: the end of aspiration? Where is the one who would draw the Border with an impudent hand with an Invincible line with his mind? Having rejected the fatal line, I will boldly throw off the earthly chain. Warmed by a fiery dream, I will rush with a renewed soul — a resident of another world — of Eternal thought to a bright abode!
